Class BTOBookingReceipt

Object
BTOBookingReceipt
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class BTOBookingReceipt extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a booking receipt generated upon a booking. This acts as a snapshot of the booking details at the time of booking which is why the attributes are copied over rather than referenced from the User and BTOProject respectively.
